snippet.title: Outworld (Apple II - Tensor Technology Inc)
snippet.description:
Outworld was an action game written by Tom Giguere and published by Tensor Technology Inc. in 1982 for the Apple ][. Hope you enjoy the short play and the memorable Beautiful Boot by Mini Appler ;)

You can find an interview about Tensor Inc. here: http://www.digitpress.com/the_digs/vic20/people/fokos.htm
